Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.97,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\blur5\pos(1196,72.667)}Terceiro fim de tarde
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:36.97,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\blur5\pos(1196,128.667)}Fígado de Peixe Sapo e Ponzu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tive um dia ruim no trabalho...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estão faltando todos os dados deste arquivo, Murasaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peço mil desculpas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.27,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H070806&\pos(996,486)}Empregado \N júnior
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.27,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H070806&\pos(108,350)}O \N culpado
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não fui nem mesmo eu que enviei o arquivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}São momentos como estes em que eu deveria apenas afogar minhas memórias na cerveja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe pela espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas hoje acho que irei afogá-las em saquê quente e fígado de peixe sapo encharcado de ponzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O vapor do peixe quente, e este saquê quente
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}fluindo tão suavemente enquanto o tempo passa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}faz com que eu me sinta tão tranquila e calma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou passar o fígado de peixe sapo! Não suporto o cheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bem, suponho que não tenha um cheiro incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entretanto, quando combinado com saquê quente...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O cheiro ruim é transformado
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}em um sabor delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Puushuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:27.94,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\i1\3c&H745AE7&\3a&H00&\frz12.24\pos(127.999,364.666)}Puushuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acho que terei que ir repreendê-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele não entende isso, cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Digo, por que eu deveria fazer o trabalho {\i1}dele{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é estúpido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Endireite-se, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu deveria tentar manter minha mente limpa amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:59.89,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0C0E09&\pos(214,78)}Fim
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:10.11,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fs72\c&H3747C8&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H00&\pos(444,500)}Wakako-zake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:14.82,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}itsumodoori no yorimichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.49,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uchi ni kaeru sono mae ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:22.18,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}hokori shiawase no aji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.09,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}kakegaenai hitotoki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:29.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}gohoubi no kaerimichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:14.82,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Desviando o meu caminho como de costume
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.49,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}antes de voltar para casa a cada dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:22.18,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Aqueles sabores deliciosos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.09,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}e experiências insubstituíveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:29.92,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Isso é o que faz este desvio tão maravilhoso.
